{"tid":1528662,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟係一位阿迷，想講幾句","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T15:28:41.000Z","uid":308020,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"056f17893cf7d40bb0995424e995b78b7be8125d","tid":1528662,"uid":308020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"（P牌仔第一次開po,希望各位唔好屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n首先，香港阿仙奴球迷會我屌你老母，以後你地唔再代表我<br />\n<br />\n其次，香港阿迷仲有好多都係有良知嘅人，希望各位唔好以偏概全<br />\n<br />\n最後，好多謝各隊球迷，真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你地，係我地阿迷欠左你地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c05abe8c3ed133ba212b4d02f10e9983965c2083","tid":1528662,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"會長一日唔落台<br />\n好難唔標籤你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6218975e036a19b862f1fb056696598efe419e9","tid":1528662,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"差佬多阿狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb8d8766e652dfb7742a6874b95cbffc86bb282","tid":1528662,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"唔企出來反你官方 有咩資格話自己係香港人？"}]}